name: Ebiblue Style V1
description:
LORA trained on the art of Ebiblue. Nice aesthetic that features more expressive faces. Check the previews for the tokens that maybe have the biggest effect.

I might retrain this (again). The file says V2, but that's because it's the second version I've trained. There was never a V1.

50 images trained on NAI and tested across multiple models. Token not required. NSFW capable (way more suited to aesthetic-looking art, though).

Images in preview may be from past versions! Do not expect full replication!

Images you make with this model and what you do with them are your responsibility!
